trans-unit.source: Represents the root element of an XML document containing the results of all files written when the <see cref="M:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.WriteAll(System.String,System.String)" /> method is invoked.
trans-unit.target: Representa o elemento raiz de um documento XML que contém os resultados de todos os arquivos gravados quando o método <see cref="M:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.WriteAll(System.String,System.String)" /> é invocado.

trans-unit.source: When you invoke the <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.WriteAll%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> method, all resolved discovery documents and a file containing a map of all those files are saved to a directory.
trans-unit.target: Quando você invoca o <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.WriteAll%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> método, todos os resolvido documentos de descoberta e um arquivo que contém um mapa de todos os arquivos são salvos em um diretório.

trans-unit.source: The map file is described in XML with the root element being <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.DiscoveryClientResultsFile>; this class is passed to the <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer> class to serialize the results.
trans-unit.target: O arquivo de mapa é descrito em XML com o elemento de raiz seja <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.DiscoveryClientResultsFile>; essa classe é passada para o <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer> classe para serializar os resultados.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.DiscoveryClientResultsFile" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.DiscoveryClientResultsFile" />.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientResultCollection" /> containing the results from a <see cref="M:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.ReadAll(System.String)" /> or <see cref="M:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.WriteAll(System.String,System.String)" /> invocation.
trans-unit.target: Um <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientResultCollection" /> que contém os resultados de uma <see cref="M:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.ReadAll(System.String)" /> ou <see cref="M:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.WriteAll(System.String,System.String)" /> invocação.
